result.adr_address: 38 Jordan Rd, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Luk Yung Vegetarian Restaurant

reviews.text: Traditional Chinese vegetarian cuisine.  Fairly priced.  Good place for small groups of people to chat and enjoy the food.
Good food, cheerful services, historical as it started business in 1968.

Great value for money! $48 for a large portion of food , plus $6/pax for nice refillable tea. 

The food does contain quite a bit of MSG , but the faux meat provides good protein for vegetarians. 

The taste was nice , food prepared in less than 10 minutes. 

They were very kind to provide a bowl of chilli sauce too! Usually you have to ask for it in other Chinese restaurants.
Delicious soup dumpling
Traditional taste of Chinese vegetarian food. They have a traditional dim sum and snack bar near the entrance of the restaurant, which is quite attractive!

result.adr_address: 香港佐敦佐敦道38號
result.name: 六榕仙館

reviews.text: 😊好吃😋的素食餐廳，廚藝好犀利👍
老牌素食館，冇花巧，傳統味道，正!
老字号，食了很多年，長輩愛豉油肚，自己愛加点糖，近期鍾愛齋义燒😋
好方便，夠大碟。又好味。
歷史悠久，出品保守，座位服務一般，沒有甚麼主題介紹，唯一是鹵味較新鮮還有一两欵甜品較好，那就是冬蓉老婆餅及合桃酥都有古方味道。。
